				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					<!--cached-Tue, 22 Jul 2014 03:18:29 +0000-->Note that a few people refer to osCommerce 2.2.1 - which is causing some confusion.<br />
<br />
2.2.1 does not exist and never has existed.<br />
<br />
2.3.1<br />
2.3.0<br />
2.2 rc2a<br />
2.2 rc2<br />
2.2 rc1<br />
2.2 ms2<br />
2.2 ms1<br />
<br />
There are more, but these would be the main osCommerce versions in use now.  I am guessing that 2.2.1 refers to 2.2 ms1.<br />
<br />
2.3.x versions of osCommerce fix a lot of insecurities that were a major downfall of 2.2 versions.  Hence why I have posted what needs to be done for each version in the post up there.  Hopefully that&#39;s understandable?
					
					<br />
					<p class='edit'>
							<strong>Edited by burt, 02 June 2011 - 11:06.</strong>
							
